{"word":"Moses","slug":"moses","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Moses</b> - (Drawn out) son of Amram, of the tribe of Levi, the leader and<p/>lawgiver of Israel<p/><b>(1)</b> General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=2'>Exo 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=10'>Exo 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=14'>Exo 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=3'>Exo 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=11'>Exo 3:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=21'>Exo 12:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14&verse=21'>Exo 14:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=20'>Exo 19:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=33&verse=11'>Exo 33:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=29'>Exo 34:29</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=29'>Num 10:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=3'>Num 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=10'>Num 20:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=3'>Num 31:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=1'>Deu 33:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=5'>Deu 34:5</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=3'>Mat 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=22'>Act 7:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=24'>Heb 11:24</a><p/><b>(2) Moses and Christ - a Parallel</b><p/>Both were preserved in childhood<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=2&verse=2'>Exo 2:2-10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=14'>Mat 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=15'>Mat 2:15</a><p/>-- Contended with masters of evil<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=11'>Exo 7:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=1'>Mat 4:1</a><p/>-- Fasted forty days<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=28'>Exo 34:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=2'>Mat 4:2</a><p/>-- Controlled the sea<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14&verse=21'>Exo 14:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=26'>Mat 8:26</a><p/>-- Fed a multitude<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=15'>Exo 16:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=20'>Mat 14:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=21'>Mat 14:21</a><p/>-- Had radiant faces<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=35'>Exo 34:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=2'>Mat 17:2</a><p/>-- Endured murmurings<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=24'>Exo 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=2'>Mar 7:2</a><p/>-- Discredited in the home<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=1'>Num 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=5'>Joh 7:5</a><p/>-- Made intercessory prayers<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=32'>Exo 32:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=17&verse=9'>Joh 17:9</a><p/>-- Spoke as oracles<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=18&verse=18'>De 18:18</a><p/>-- Had seventy helpers<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=16'>Num 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=17'>Num 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=1'>Luk 10:1</a><p/>-- Established memorials<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=14'>Exo 12:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=19'>Luk 22:19</a><p/>-- Re-appeared after death<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=3'>Mat 17:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=3'>Act 1:3</a><p/><b>MOSES' ROD</b> <b>SEE</b> Rod, ROD OF MOSES"}]}